# Tether repository .gitignore. See plan.md §1.1.

# ── Build artefacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
build/
node_modules/
*.bin
*.elf
*.map
.pio/
sdkconfig
sdkconfig.old
dependencies.lock

# ── Coverage ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
coverage/
cover.out
*.cover.out
*.coverprofile

# ── Generated proto code (intentionally committed; do not ignore) ───────
# go/pkg/protocol/protocolpb/*.pb.go is committed on purpose so that
# builds do not require protoc locally.

# ── Agent loop state ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.phase-state
logs/
.agent-loop.lock

# ── OS / editor noise ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/
.idea/
cov.out
go/forge.cov
go/cli.cov

# Go tool binaries (built ad-hoc; never commit)
go/tetherd
go/tools/tether-loopback/tether-loopback
go/tools/tether-e2e/tether-e2e
go/tools/tether-voice-test/tether-voice-test
go/tools/tether-matrix-test/tether-matrix-test
